# Scheduled Execution
A GitHub Actions workflow is included to support scheduled data ingestion and simulate automated pipeline updates.

# Notes
- The system simulates live customer data by adding new data batches  
- SQLite is used for structured storage of historical and incoming customer data  
- The focus is on pipeline design, reproducibility, and deployment  
- Logs and artifacts are stored for monitoring and reproducibility